Class StringIndexedCsvRecord

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.records.AbstractBaseRecord
      gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.records.StringIndexedCsvRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:
IndexedFieldsRecord<String>, ModifiableIndexedFieldsRecord<String>, Record
public class StringIndexedCsvRecord
extends AbstractBaseRecord
implements ModifiableIndexedFieldsRecord<String>

CsvRecord is a record of a comma separated values (CSV) file.
The default separator is semicolon, but it is possible to change the separator to any character.
